Package com.annomarket.job

Classes related to job management.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InputDetails
    A single input specification for an annotation job.
    InputDetails.CommonCrawlDetails
    "Struct" class holding details of a Common Crawl search.
    InputSummary
    Summary information about an input specification.
    Job
    Full details of an annotation job, and methods to configure and control the job.
    JobManager
    Main entry point to the job management API to manage annotation jobs you have reserved.
    JobResult
    A single result file produced by a job.
    JobSummary
    Summary information about a single annotation job.
    LogMessage
    "Struct" class representing a timestamped log message.
    Output
    A single output specification for an annotation job.
